<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Dein Shop – Benachrichtigung</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: #181f2a;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      background: rgba(17,25,40,0.92);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    }
    .email-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .email-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #a5b4fc;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .email-content {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .classic-card {
      background: rgba(31,41,55,0.97);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      border: 1.5px solid #6366f1;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #aaa;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1, #60a5fa 90%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 1.2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <div class="email-title">Danke für deine Bestellung!</div>
    </div>
    <div class="email-content">
      Hallo <b><%= username %></b>,<br>
      vielen Dank für deinen Einkauf in unserem Shop.<br>
      Hier sind deine Bestelldetails:
    </div>
    <div class="classic-card">
      <b>Produkt:</b> <%= productName %><br>
      <b>Lizenz/Key:</b> <%= licenseKey %><br>
      <b>Bestelldatum:</b> <%= orderDate %>
    </div>
    <a href="<%= shopUrl %>" class="btn">Zum Shop</a>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= year %> Dein Shop – Vielen Dank für dein Vertrauen!
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 